title.rendered: Vienna Compact Two Tier Workstation with Stylish  Feature Frame and Upper Storage Shelf – home office

content.rendered:
Our Vienna Compact Two Tier Workstation with Stylish  Feature Frame and Upper Storage Shelf is perfect for the home office!

Made with 15mm Melamine wood effect laminate and a steel frame. 

Three open storage compartments and complementing upper shelf

Assembly required. 3 year warranty. Price is for desk only.
